CHECKLIST FOR NEW RELEASES
==========================

* Update CHANGES
* Update lm_sensors.lsm
* Do a `make package'
* Tag the release using CVS ('cvs tag V#-#-#' from the dist root)
* Do a `cvs commit' (to commit the new version changes)
* Move new release to web archive, and pgp sign (& copy to mirrors)
* Freshmeat announce
